			<div id="artTitles">
				<h1 id="artibodyTitle">吐蕃“尚论掣逋突瞿”考释</h1>
				<h2 id="artisubTitle">——《新唐书·吐蕃传》误载举隅</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="articl_info">
